.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite, water
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, plum, zucchini
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, bike, ship, motorbike
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, parkour, surfing
 1. the person drinking fanta is the person eating corn##1
 2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 3. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 4. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is the person driving the bike##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
11. the person drinking sprite is the person eating zucchini##1
12. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | water       | sprite   | fanta   | iced-tea   |
| Food       | lime        | zucchini | corn    | plum       |
| Transport      | motorbike | bike    | ship  | boat |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | parkour  | cycling | surfing    |

